{"tid":1812680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔行山人士被黃蜂針傷七人送院","createTime":"2020-01-05T16:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T07:56:48.000Z","uid":35348,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3d930df8b379306200346302a7298cfc54434532","tid":1812680,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一批行山人士下午在大埔懷疑被黃蜂針傷，至少七人需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n部分傷者由救護車送往大埔那打素醫院治理，他們大部分都是手腳受傷，有兩名傷者自行駕車前往醫院求醫。<br />\n<br />\n下午三時許，一批行山人士途經八仙嶺自然教育徑一條山邊小徑時，被懷疑黃蜂襲擊，有事主指當時現場有超過一百隻黃蜂。由於有多人報稱受傷，多輛救護車奉召到場處理。"},{"pid":"ca6e34fab786624f03f31aefda899fd6e35b4530","tid":1812680,"uid":15886,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"N賓 連黃蜂都出埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629e3953b462898d177d1d5ba566adc8374b6500","tid":1812680,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a09bbc8315fd47ea77c9d2a943d3bcf8bcc9a92","tid":1812680,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:13:09.000Z","msg":"沖完涼未"},{"pid":"4ed73daee23bd62eb238f5e4a617623d135cdcd8","tid":1812680,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70023f5fa69b9ef11f404a0cdc9743bba996ddfb","tid":1812680,"uid":234509,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"N bee<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12aed4da5fd367c10892983f5c803c5031e009cb","tid":1812680,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a09bbc8315fd47ea77c9d2a943d3bcf8bcc9a92","tid":1812680,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16: