"uid":15886,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"N賓 連黃蜂都出埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"咪25啦感情台狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"自抽都唔比？"},{"pid":"312238210421e8dc7966479599e833c16782fee4","tid":1812680,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"廢蜂"},{"pid":"14cf3140fbc4164d2152a85a2b42e353b2b4a9a8","tid":1812680,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"有用po <br />\n推"},{"pid":"b3fabd917705875f687d3f54525671f7bcd52d8b","tid":1812680,"uid":197474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"廢鋒剩係識針人"},{"pid":"78b64b25d9715080c45037805e86df09bca32a17","tid":1812680,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"黃之蜂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae1a0ce020af6eb68a34c713bacd9dd93f1b08e","tid":1812680,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629e3953b462898d177d1d5ba566adc8374b6500","tid":1812680,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:26:36.000Z","msg":"<em>不論平地與山尖，無限風光盡被佔。<br />\n採得百花成蜜後，爲誰辛苦爲誰甜。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">⸺羅隱</div></em>"},{"pid":"119e5992a092a5a60ce3333a6415ea3956412479","tid":1812680,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"蕭粵中稱，黃蜂有別於蜜蜂，後者用螫針叮人只可用一次，黃蜂能把身上的螫針縮回體內反覆使用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因此如被黃蜂螫傷，毋須花時間找出螫針，可立即使用冷敷或冰袋，幫助減輕痛楚及紓緩腫脹，建議盡快求醫。<br />\n<br />\n如被蜜蜂螫傷，則應盡快移除螫針再冷敷及求醫。但注意移除螫針時，切勿用手指緊捏螫針，否則有機會令螫針內毒液進入皮膚。<br />\n<br />\n先護頭 直線行走勿大叫<br />\n當被黃蜂襲擊時，最重要是保護頭部。遇到黃蜂時，可先以衣物或背包包裹頭部以作保護，並沿直線行走，遠離蜂群。蕭粵中提醒，行走時不宜大叫及做出用手撥開黃蜂的挑釁動作，否則有可能增加被黃蜂襲擊的風險。"},{"pid":"b3de9b02f2ceb2c097cacbfd197a0569c73469da","tid":1812680,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"「黃蜂可以針完再針，蜜蜂針完就會死，蜂針留在人體皮膚」，如不慎被蜂群針到，宜先進行局部治理，留意患處有否遺留蜂針，如有可利用硬卡紙或信用卡挑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，切勿用手擠出蜂針，因蜂針可能藏有毒素，萬一處理不當可令毒素進入皮膚。"},{"pid":"99d1a8cacb4fc66c2a3642a4f1b0632daf1ca9ea","tid":1812680,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca6e34fab786624f03f31aefda899fd6e35b4530","tid":1812680,"uid":15886,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"N賓 連黃蜂都出埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:36:08.000Z","msg":"據悉，事件中亦有多名深圳來港行山人士被黃蜂螫中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，事後在八仙嶺山腳的船灣遊客中心等候，由救護員初步治理被蜂針螫中傷口後，陸續送院，其中有2名男子需要抬床入院，但仍清醒，其餘人士大部均可自行步入醫院。"},{"pid":"db730096ec184a57288828e74a297708eb965e88","tid":1812680,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2534082/bee_thumb_20200105_D_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2534082%2Fbee_thumb_20200105_D_1024.jpg&h=687672bc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}